About 

“We should continually be striving to transform every art into a science: in the process, we advance the art..”
-Donald Knuth

Terpsicore Systems is a rapidly growing software development company from Latin America.

The team was assembled in the summer of year 2011 by a group of academically driven achievers looking to put into practice their passion for mathematics, electronics and computer science. Since then, the group has evolved  through enthusiastic work and positive feedback into a consolidated firm.

Our customers have chosen us to bring their ideas to life in the areas of :

Operations Research
Custom Software development

